data.name: XShapeArranger
desc: Objects implementing this interface can be used to arrange Shapes.

methods.name: arrange
desc: applies the specified Arrangement to the specified collection of Shapes.

methods.name: bringToFront
desc: moves the specified Shapes by a specified number of objects more to the front.

methods.name: reverseOrder
desc: reverses the order of the specified collection of Shapes.

methods.name: sendToBack
desc: moves the specified Shapes nSteps objects more to the back.

methods.name: setBehindShape
desc: moves the specified collection of Shapes behind the specified single Shape.

methods.name: setInFrontOf
desc: moves the specified collection of Shapes in front of the specified single Shape.
